OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FA woman from Sussex who was sexually
OL,7,Fabused as a child and then later raped
OL,8,Fas a young girl and a teenager has
OL,9,Fwelcomed a new service that aims to
OL,10,Fensure that survivors of sexual
OL,11,Foffences are provided with the highest
OL,12,Fquality of care and support.
OL,14,FMichelle, now aged 56, has waived her
OL,15,Fright to anonymity.
OL,17,FShe has spoken about her terrifying
OL,18,Fexperience of reporting the abuse to
OL,19,Fpolice. Even though an adult was
OL,20,Fpresent, she says it was traumatic.
