OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FMichelle says:
OL,8,F"I feel very passionately about how
OL,9,Fimportant it is to change the way
OL,10,Fthings are done within the legal
OL,11,Fsystem. With the police, with the
OL,12,Fcourts. There needs to be so much more
OL,13,Fawareness on such a delicate subject.
OL,14,FMost times when someone is reporting
OL,15,Fthey are going to be very traumatised.
OL,16,FThey need to walk into an environment
OL,17,Fwhere they feel safe and they feel
OL,18,Fheard. And they are supported all the
OL,19,Fway through. "
