OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FThe new scheme, called FIDES, has been
OL,7,Flaunched by Sussex Police.
OL,9,FIt comes 18 months after ITV News
OL,10,FMeridian revealed that only 3% of
OL,11,FSussex Police investigations into
OL,12,Fsexual offences resulted in a
OL,13,Fprosecution.
OL,15,FEight new Victim Support Co-ordinators
OL,16,Fwill act as a single point of contact
OL,17,Ffor survivors, build a rapport with
OL,18,Fthem and help to develop an
OL,19,Funderstanding of what barriers exist
OL,20,Fin reporting and where possible
OL,21,Fsupport a prosecution.
