OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FMichelle now volunteers with Survivors
OL,7,FNetwork, a charity that supports
OL,8,Fwomen, men, transgender and non-
OL,9,Fbionary people and teenagers. She says
OL,10,Fshe hopes the new service will
OL,11,Fcontinue to build compassionate
OL,12,Fbridges with courageous souls who
OL,13,Freach out for help and report.
OL,15,F"The better the process for the person
OL,16,Fwho is reporting, the more help they
OL,17,Fget. The more they are made to feel
OL,18,Flistened to. That will be invaluable.
