OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FThe aim of Victim Support Co-
OL,7,Fordinators is to alleviate the volume
OL,8,Fof cases currently held by specialist
OL,9,Frape investigation officers so they
OL,10,Fcan concentrate on achieving
OL,11,Fprosecutions, develop trust and
OL,12,Fconfidence with victims and ultimately
OL,13,Fsupport an increase in positive
OL,14,Foutcomes and improved conviction rates.
