OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FThe new VCs, who have recently
OL,7,Fcompleted their initial training and
OL,8,Fare now in post, will specifically
OL,9,Ffocus on these cases and will also
OL,10,Fhave additional training in areas such
OL,11,Fas domestic abuse, neurodiversity, and
OL,12,FBlack heritage.
OL,14,FIt's hoped it will help them to best
OL,15,Fmeet a more diverse range of needs.
OL,17,FIf you or someone you know is in need
OL,18,Fof support, you can contact the
